lead_paragraph: A 48-year-old man who had said, "I love to kill," after murdering three strangers, was executed here early today. The inmate, Keith Williams, was injected with lethal drugs at 12:03 A.M. at San Quentin State Prison. Mr. Williams was declared dead five minutes later. The Supreme Court had denied his appeal two hours earlier.

headline.main: The Killer Of 3 Strangers Is Executed
